  Calificaciones <i data-feather="star" class="feather-12 tx-warning filled tx-warning filled"></i><span class="tx-warning"><%= @gig.score_average.round(1) %> <small class="tx-gray-600 tx-10">(<%= @gig.score_times %>) | </small></span> <a class="mg-l-5" data-toggle="collapse" href="#reviewsGig" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="reviewsGig">Ver reseñas</a>
